<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 08:10:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“杰出的年轻人”：佛罗里达州高中橄榄球运动员钱斯·盖纳在比赛中倒地后死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/exceptional-young-man-florida-high-school-football-player-chance-gainer-dies-after-collapsing-during-game/articleshow/113163454.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113163454.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;来自佛罗里达州的 18 岁高中橄榄球运动员 Chance Gainer 在佐治亚州的一场比赛中不幸倒地身亡。他最近访问了范德比尔特大学，希望在那里踢足球。盖纳在突然去世前两次达阵。随着当局的调查，他倒地的原因仍不清楚。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 07:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/exceptional-young-man-florida-high-school-football-player-chance-gainer-dies-after-collapsing-during-game/articleshow/113163454.cms</guid></item><item><title>“哈里在英国仍有主力”：王子与家人的“秘密”联系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/harry-still-has-an-anchor-in-the-uk-princes-secret-connection-with-family-members/articleshow/113163307.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113163307.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管与威廉王子和查尔斯国王疏远，哈里王子仍然与已故母亲戴安娜王妃的家人保持联系。他参加了简·费罗斯夫人丈夫的葬礼，并与叔叔查尔斯·斯宾塞一起住在奥尔索普别墅。此外，他与表弟比阿特丽斯公主保持着良好的关系，她在他和威廉之间进行调解。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 06:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/harry-still-has-an-anchor-in-the-uk-princes-secret-connection-with-family-members/articleshow/113163307.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国总统拜登离任532天，4年请假48年</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-spent-532-days-away-from-office-took-48-years-worth-of-leave-in-4-years/articleshow/113162558.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113162558.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登在不到四年的时间里休假了532天，远远超过了他的前任。批评者认为，他的频繁缺席忽视了通货膨胀和边境安全等关键问题。虽然助手们声称他在假期期间远程工作，但他放松的公开形象引发了关于平衡总统职责与个人休假的争论。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 06:23:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-spent-532-days-away-from-office-took-48-years-worth-of-leave-in-4-years/articleshow/113162558.cms</guid></item><item><title>委内瑞拉反对派前总统候选人为何逃离该国：关键细节</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-venezuelan-opposition-ex-presidential-candidate-fled-the-country-key-details/articleshow/113162204.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113162204.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;委内瑞拉反对派领导人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯在有争议的总统选举结果有利于尼古拉斯·马杜罗后因逮捕令躲藏起来，在西班牙寻求庇护。委内瑞拉允许他安全离开该国，强调遵守国际法，并致力于在与巴西持续紧张的外交紧张局势中实现政治和平。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 05:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-venezuelan-opposition-ex-presidential-candidate-fled-the-country-key-details/articleshow/113162204.cms</guid></item><item><title>乔治亚州枪击案嫌疑人的母亲在枪击前几分钟给学校打电话，警告“极端紧急情况”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-shooter-suspects-mother-called-school-minutes-before-shooting-warned-of-extreme-emergency/articleshow/113161025.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113161025.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在乔治亚州校园枪击事件发生之前，玛西·格雷向学校辅导员通报了她儿子柯尔特的情况。玛西通过柯尔特发来的短信联系了学校。阿巴拉奇高中发生枪击事件，造成四人死亡、九人受伤。柯尔特和他的父亲都面临严重的法律指控。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 05:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-shooter-suspects-mother-called-school-minutes-before-shooting-warned-of-extreme-emergency/articleshow/113161025.cms</guid></item><item><title>因公众愤怒，澳大利亚 2026 年人口普查将纳入 LGBTIQ+ 身份问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australias-2026-census-to-include-lgbtiq-identity-questions-following-public-outrage/articleshow/113161949.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113161949.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚 2026 年人口普查将首次包括针对 16 岁及以上个人的性取向和性别的可选问题。这一决定是在他们最初被排除在外引起争议之后作出的。政府官员强调，这一变化旨在确保 LGBTIQ+ 群体的代表性，反映他们在国家统计数据中的重要性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 05:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australias-2026-census-to-include-lgbtiq-identity-questions-following-public-outrage/articleshow/113161949.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国男子工作104天休息1天身亡 公司追究责任</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-man-dies-after-working-for-104-days-with-1-day-off-company-held-liable/articleshow/113161351.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113161351.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 30岁的画家阿宝，在连续104天只休息一天的艰苦工作后，因多脏器衰竭去世。法院判决该公司承担20%的责任，并责令其家属赔偿。他的工作条件违反了中国劳动法关于工作时间的规定。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 04:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-man-dies-after-working-for-104-days-with-1-day-off-company-held-liable/articleshow/113161351.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我们是由愚蠢的人统治的”：特朗普呼吁修改宪法以罢免“密谋”副总统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/were-run-by-stupid-people-trump-calls-for-constitutional-change-to-remove-conspiring-vice-presidents/articleshow/113160223.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160223.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普提议修改第25条修正案，罢免掩盖总统无能的副总统。这一呼吁是在威斯康星州的一次竞选集会上做出的，是为了回应乔·拜登糟糕的辩论表现以及随后退出总统竞选，卡马拉·哈里斯因此成为民主党提名人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/were-run-by-stupid-people-trump-calls-for-constitutional-change-to-remove-conspiring-vice-presidents/articleshow/113160223.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国圣贝纳迪诺气温突破三位数，肆虐的野火迫使人们疏散</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/raging-wildfire-forces-evacuations-in-us-san-bernardino-as-temperatures-cross-triple-digits/articleshow/113160573.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160573.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;洛杉矶附近的圣贝纳迪诺国家森林发生野火，气温高达 112°F，导致人员疏散。星期四晚上发生的线火已经烧毁了 11 平方英里的植被。超过 500 名消防员在空中支援下赶赴现场。官员警告说，未来 12 小时内火势可能会严重蔓延。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:59:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/raging-wildfire-forces-evacuations-in-us-san-bernardino-as-temperatures-cross-triple-digits/articleshow/113160573.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国认为伊朗已向俄罗斯转让短程弹道导弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia/articleshow/113160521.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160521.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国认为伊朗已向俄罗斯转让短程弹道导弹用于乌克兰战争，引发了对冲突升级和欧洲安全威胁的担忧。白宫重申对此类转让的警告，而伊朗则否认提供武器，并呼吁停火。中央情报局局长强调了涉及俄罗斯、中国、伊朗和朝鲜的令人不安的防务关系。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia/articleshow/113160521.cms</guid></item><item><title>卡玛拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普将在首场辩论中对峙：规则是什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-and-donald-trump-to-face-off-in-first-debate-what-are-the-rules/articleshow/113160440.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160440.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡马拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普将于 9 月 10 日进行首次直接辩论。这场辩论由 ABC 新闻在费城国家宪法中心主办，时长 90 分钟，包括定时回答和静音麦克风，以确保辩论顺利进行。辩论将在全国范围内转播，没有现场观众。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:39:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-and-donald-trump-to-face-off-in-first-debate-what-are-the-rules/articleshow/113160440.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 透露了 SpaceX 将无人驾驶星际飞船送往火星的雄心勃勃的计划：我们所知道的</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-reveals-spacexs-ambitious-plan-to-send-uncrewed-starships-to-mars-what-we-know/articleshow/113160287.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160287.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃隆·马斯克宣布，SpaceX 将在两年内向火星发射第一艘无人驾驶星际飞船，旨在测试其着陆可靠性。如果成功，载人任务将在四年内进行。最终目标是在大约 20 年内在火星上建立一座自给自足的城市。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-reveals-spacexs-ambitious-plan-to-send-uncrewed-starships-to-mars-what-we-know/articleshow/113160287.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗特勤局特工因在欧洲范围内密谋杀害犹太人而在法国被拘留</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/iranian-secret-service-agents-detained-in-france-for-europe-wide-plot-to-kill-jews/articleshow/113160024.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160024.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; Abdelkrim S 和 Sabrina B 因涉嫌参与伊朗支持的针对德国和法国犹太人的暗杀阴谋而受到巴黎一家法院的指控。这对夫妇被指控与恐怖组织合谋，目前被审前拘留。调查还将其与对以色列企业的纵火企图联系起来。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/iranian-secret-service-agents-detained-in-france-for-europe-wide-plot-to-kill-jews/articleshow/113160024.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国肯塔基州高速公路多人遭枪击，追捕“武装”嫌疑人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/multiple-people-shot-along-highway-in-us-state-of-kentucky-hunt-for-armed-suspect-on/articleshow/113159936.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113159936.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在肯塔基州南部，75 号州际公路的一段路段因枪击事件而关闭，造成多人受伤。当局正在寻找嫌疑人约瑟夫·库奇，他被认为携带武器且危险。劳雷尔县治安官办公室和肯塔基州警方建议居民在追捕嫌疑人期间留在室内。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 01:21:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/multiple-people-shot-along-highway-in-us-state-of-kentucky-hunt-for-armed-suspect-on/articleshow/113159936.cms</guid></item><item><title>佐治亚州校园枪击案嫌疑人柯尔特·格雷在案发前曾住在几处出租房中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-suspect-colt-gray-lived-in-several-rental-homes-prior-to-the-incident/articleshow/113159693.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113159693.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 14 岁犯罪嫌疑人柯尔特·格雷 (Colt Gray) 和他的父亲科林 (Colin) 因在佐治亚州阿巴拉奇高中杀害两名学生和两名教师而面临指控。科林离婚后，一家人多次搬家。柯尔特饱受欺凌和父母分居的困扰。他因这起事件而作为成年人接受审判。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 00:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-suspect-colt-gray-lived-in-several-rental-homes-prior-to-the-incident/articleshow/113159693.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈里王子将在 40 岁后获得主要遗产。他将得到......</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-set-to-receive-major-inheritance-after-he-turns-40-he-will-get-/articleshow/113157399.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157399.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈里王子将于 9 月 15 日庆祝他的 40 岁生日，他将从一个家庭信托基金中收到约 800 万英镑。该基金由他的曾祖母于 1994 年设立，旨在为她的曾孙提供经济礼物。通过与 Spotify、Netflix 的交易和图书合同，这对夫妇的财富不断增加，财务上的增长也随之增加。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-set-to-receive-major-inheritance-after-he-turns-40-he-will-get-/articleshow/113157399.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国MQ-9无人机在也门马里布省被胡塞武装击落</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-mq-9-drone-shot-down-by-houthis-in-yemens-marib-governorate/articleshow/113157558.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157558.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;与伊朗结盟的胡塞组织声称对击落也门马里卜省上空的一架美国 MQ-9 无人机负责，称该无人机正在进行敌对活动。这一事件与胡塞武装在红海和亚丁湾持续袭击船只有关，因为他们要求结束加沙的以色列与哈马斯冲突。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-mq-9-drone-shot-down-by-houthis-in-yemens-marib-governorate/articleshow/113157558.cms</guid></item><item><title>佐治亚州校园枪击事件：欺凌和家庭斗争如何导致四人死亡的悲剧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-how-bullying-and-family-struggles-led-to-tragedy-that-killed-four/articleshow/113158183.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113158183.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名 14 岁男孩和他的父亲因在佐治亚州阿巴拉奇高中发生致命枪击事件而面临指控，该枪击案造成四人死亡。此案凸显了这名少年的家庭生活陷入困境、持续受到欺凌，以及他父亲在让他获得枪支方面所扮演的角色。两人于 2023 年 9 月首次出庭。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 22:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-how-bullying-and-family-struggles-led-to-tragedy-that-killed-four/articleshow/113158183.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦陆军参谋长首次承认其在 1999 年卡吉尔战争中发挥了直接作用</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pak-army-admits-involvement-in-kargil-war/articleshow/113156851.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113156851.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦陆军参谋长阿西姆·穆尼尔将军承认，他的军队直接参与了 1999 年针对印度的卡吉尔战争，结束了长期以来只有克什米尔本土叛军参与战斗的说法。他向在冲突中阵亡的巴基斯坦士兵致敬，并承认他们在之前的战争中为国家和伊斯兰教做出的牺牲。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 18:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pak-army-admits-involvement-in-kargil-war/articleshow/113156851.cms</guid></item><item><title>一位街头艺术家记录了乌克兰的战争，一次一幅鲜明的壁画</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-street-artist-documents-war-in-ukraine-one-stark-mural-at-a-time/articleshow/113157179.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157179.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰街头艺术家 Gamlet Zinkivskyi 加入了一支保卫哈尔科夫的志愿部队，但他的指挥官建议他改为绘画。他在被炸毁的街道上创作的壁画描绘了战时现实，鼓舞了士兵和平民的士气。尽管受到广泛赞赏，但他的一些作品因其主题而受到批评。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 19:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-street-artist-documents-war-in-ukraine-one-stark-mural-at-a-time/articleshow/113157179.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>